<refsect1 id="GtkBorderCombo.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
It is a <link linkend="GtkComboBox"><type>GtkComboBox</type></link> subclass with a variety of border styles in the popdown window arranged in a table of togglebuttons.</para>
<para>
